rows.label: tlk45500152_03_msg0001
rows.name: Let me tell you about my dream.

rows.label: tlk45500152_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I love board games like nothing else.
Play them with the kids every night.

rows.label: tlk45500152_03_msg0003
rows.name:
So one day, I'd like to buy all the
products in Elgeschel Hobby Store
and become the store's owner myself!

rows.label: tlk45500152_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Course, even as the owner you don't
get to buy their stuff for free. But it'd
be something to boast about, right?!
